item.description: Chunghwa Telecom NOKIA G-040W-Q Firewall function does not block ICMP TIMESTAMP requests by default, an unauthenticated remote attacker can exploit this vulnerability by sending a crafted package, resulting in partially sensitive information exposed to an actor.
